<style>
  .riccio-manifesto {
    padding: 10rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--riccio-ivory, #FAFAF8);
  }

  .riccio-manifesto__inner {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Italic serif title — exactly like Hermès "Sur le départ" */
  .riccio-manifesto__title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', serif;
    font-size: 5.2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: #1A1714;
    margin: 0 0 2.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .riccio-manifesto__text {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.85;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: rgba(26, 23, 20, 0.7);
    max-width: 56rem;
    margin: 0 auto 3.2rem;
  }

  /* Hermès-style CTA: small caps, underline, no box */
  .riccio-manifesto__cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #1A1714;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1A1714;
    padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .riccio-manifesto__cta:hover {
    opacity: 0.45;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .riccio-manifesto {
      padding: 7rem 2.4rem;
    }
    .riccio-manifesto__title {
      font-size: 3.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="riccio-manifesto scroll-trigger animate--fade-in">
  <div class="riccio-manifesto__inner">
    <h2 class="riccio-manifesto__title">L'art de vivre<br>par Riccio</h2>
    <p class="riccio-manifesto__text">
      Chaque objet Riccio naît d'une conviction profonde : le quotidien mérite d'être beau.
      Nos créations en cuir tressé, façonnées avec un soin extrême, transforment les gestes
      les plus simples en instants d'élégance véritable.
    </p>
    <a href="/collections/stressa" class="riccio-manifesto__cta">Explorer la maison</a>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Riccio — Manifeste",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section-riccio-manifesto",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Riccio — Manifeste" }]
}
{% endschema %}
